note: Enjoying connecting with people here. I'm interested in history, science, art, archaeology, farming, linguistics, justice work, and religion. Copyeditor, quilter, darner, birder, winter lover, pluviophile, night-sky watcher, cloud admirer. She/her. I live in New Jersey.
